Name: Jumpin' Tanks
About the game: Jumpin' Tanks is a multiplayer 2D platformer where players can enjoy various game modes of arcade fun! Duke it out in Free-For-All to see which player will be the last tank standing. Eliminate the infected tanks in Pandemic or risk being infected yourself. Team up with your friends in Versus and see which squad will come out on top.
